# Root-context images: the private MkDocs site and the Quill web frontend.
# Keep the build context limited to their Dockerfiles and the specific
# reviewed content/vendored assets each one needs.
*
!hi-orbit-wiki/
!hi-orbit-wiki/mkdocs.yml
!hi-orbit-wiki/docs/
!hi-orbit-wiki/docs/**
!wiki-site/
!wiki-site/Dockerfile
!single-compose/
!single-compose/nginx.orbot-quill.conf
!vendor/kst-beta-ide/
!vendor/kst-beta-ide/writer/
!vendor/kst-beta-ide/writer/**
